commit.message: Clean up and remove debug code
Clarify purpose of test by...adding a smiley!

Correct axis tick behaviour.

Before, tickvalues would be filtered, but the `tickFormat()` function would not know this,
and it would just iterate over the original ones, so all ticks would be displaced. Now,
we always take filtering into account. Maybe this commit introduces a regression, I hope not!
Clean up text_axis.py a bit, just style things
